1 b. Clearly state the rights being waived in exchange for the premium discount,
2 including the right to a trial by jury; and
3 c. Include the following statement in at least twelve-point bold font:
4 "By signing this form, I agree to resolve all covered property insurance claims
5 through mandatory binding arbitration. I understand that by agreeing to
6 mandatory binding arbitration:
7 I am giving up my right to have disputes resolved in court.
8 I am giving up my right to a jury trial.
9 I am accepting these terms in exchange for a premium discount of [dollar amount
